Awkward=rara
Has an awkward taste and is used for brewing potions.=Tiene un sabor extraño y se utiliza para preparar pociones.
Mundane=vulgar
Has a terrible taste and is not really useful for brewing potions.=
Thick=densa
Has a bitter taste and is not really useful for brewing potions.=
